|2 |  ├─DISTRIBUTED TABLE GET        |a   |1       |5           |
|3 |  └─SORT                         |    |3       |9           |
|4 |    └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE FULL SCAN|b   |3       |9           |
=================================================================
